$ Excel: Data -> Data Tools -> Data Validation

Define (so called → Microsoft/Office/Excel/GUI/Ribbon/tabs/Data/Data-Tools/Data-Validation[data validation]) rules that limit the values that can be entered into a
→ Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/Range/cell or → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/Range[range].

sa:
  In → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model[Excel's Object Model], such rules can be created with a → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/Validation[`validation` object].

  → Microsoft/Office/Excel/GUI/formatting/conditional[Conditional formatting]
